Results.ReviewText: Always loved  nescafe as a brand and really enjoyed the rich smoothness of nescafe gold blend and the best bit is when you pull back the seal and get the pure pleasure of the aroma of a great coffee.
Results.Title: Smooth

Results.ReviewText: I bought this coffee about a week ago and my family have commented several times regarding the lovely smooth taste and aroma. This will be one of my regular purchases from now on. Highly recommended.
Results.Title: One of the best

Results.ReviewText: Bought this a while a go when on offer and have never went back to my old bran! Fresh strong coffee every time love to see it on offer in the supermarket as i stock up my cupboard for weeks at a time
Results.Title: Awakeness

Results.ReviewText: Tried this today and found that it is comparable to my favourite Gold Blend which is the Barista style coffee which I treat myself to every now and again, won't have to any more can just by this one
Results.Title: Tried today

ClientResponses.Response: Hi, thanks very much for letting us know your thoughts on the new recipe. We really appreciate your feedback! The residue you can see at the bottom of your cup is micro ground coffee that was added to NESCAFÉ Gold Blend during the recent change. This is non-soluble coffee and gives you a similar experience to that of a barista made coffee!

Results.ReviewText: I have drunk Gold Blend for years and now with new packaging comes a disgusting after taste and a brown silt at the bottom of the cup!! What on earth have you done to this once great tasting coffee?
Results.Title: What have you done?

Results.ReviewText: We've drunk Gold Blend on and off for ages, and though there are others that do very well , Gold Blend is always reliable.  Not real coffee it is true, but as instant coffee goes can be depended on.
Results.Title: Gold Blend still bringing it home

Results.ReviewText: I have been drinking Nescafe Gold Blend or many years and I love it, I am sorry to say your new jars are so slippery that the last jar slipped straight out of my hands on to the floor not Happy !!!
Results.Title: Lovely coffee But .......

Results.ReviewText: I bought this two weeks ago.  However unlike  the previous jar I find the new style leaves a slight sediment in the bottom of the cup which I do not like and I did not find the taste any different.
Results.Title: Good taste

Results.ReviewText: I love this coffee it is the only instant coffee I have found that doesn't taste like instant! I've given up using my cafetiere as this is just as good as ground coffee without the mess afterwards.
Results.Title: Love this coffee not like instant at all

Results.ReviewText: buy this coffee all the time i wont drink any other coffee there nothing like the rich smooth taste and a great price last for nearly 2 weeks for me the new design is awesome much eaiser to handle.

ClientResponses.Response: Thanks very much for taking the time to let us know your thoughts on the recipe change. We really appreciate your feedback & will be passing your comments to the rest of the team.

Results.ReviewText: Was never really a coffee person, decided to try Nescafe Gold, and haven't gone back. I love coffee and it has really opened my senses up to try all types of coffee, I enjoy all blends of Nescafe.

ClientResponses.Response: Hi, it's sad to hear you're not enjoying the new recipe. The residue you can see at the bottom of your cup is micro ground coffee that was added to NESCAFÉ Gold Blend during the recent change. This is non-soluble coffee and gives you a similar experience to that of a barista made coffee! We've made a note of your comments & will pass them to the rest of the team.

Results.ReviewText: sorry but I do not like the new blend - bought gold blend for years as family favourite. Nobody here will drink it now. A bitter taste and residue in the bottom of the mug. Please change it back.

Results.ReviewText: Lovely and smooth taste, not bitter like some instant coffees.  Went over to a cheaper brand recently but have returned and can really taste the difference.  Good offers in many stores lately too

Results.ReviewText:
I love the new shaped jar. The taste is still great although seems slightly harsher.
Value for money has been fantastic lately as there have been many promotions.
It is still my regular coffee.

Results.ReviewText: Bought this last week after having a review of my coffee drinking habits and glad that i did. Really great taste for an instant and not to expensive over own brand products. Definitely recommend.
Results.Title: Nescafe Gold Blend!!!!!

Results.ReviewText: I have long been a fan of Nescafe Gold Blend. I look forward each day to my refreshment break and its accompanying aroma and  inexpensive delicious drink the effects of which linger all morning.

As an avid coffee lover and having tried many different coffees this is my absolute favourite. It's creamy tasty and smells delicious. I will stay faithful to this coffee for eternity 
Enjoy <3

Liked gold blend as it didnt have much hickory taste but now I can even taste that !
